                java.lang.Double filterValue,
                java.lang.Integer yearOverlapThreshold,
                NoDataLabel noDataLabel)
        New simplified constructor for FHAES GUI
        Parameters:
        inputFileArray - - files to process
        startYear - - start of year range to process
        endYear - - end of year range to process
        filterType - - composite filter type (number of fires or percentage)
        eventTypeToProcess - - whether to do calculations on injuries or fires
        filterValue - - composite filter value
        yearOverlapThreshold - - number of years that must overlap between two sites
        noDataLabel - - Label to use when comparison is not possible
